article.description: — Josh Corbin's 34 points led Robert Morris over Fairleigh Dickinson 97-86 on Sunday.
article.headline: Corbin scores 34, Robert Morris takes down Fairleigh Dickinson 97-86
article.linkText: Corbin scores 34, Robert Morris takes down Fairleigh Dickinson 97-86
article.story: MOON TOWNSHIP, Pa. -- — Josh Corbin's 34 points led Robert Morris over Fairleigh Dickinson 97-86 on Sunday. Corbin shot 8 for 16 (7 for 14 from 3-point range) and 11 of 11 from the free throw line for the Colonials (2-4). Justice Williams scored 21 points and added eight rebounds. TJ Wainwright was 5 of 7 shooting and 10 of 10 from the free throw line to finish with 20 points. Sean Moore finished with 21 points, nine rebounds and three steals for the Knights (4-4). Ansley Almonor added 18 points and six rebounds for Fairleigh Dickinson. In addition, Heru Bligen finished with 14 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
